dmca.title: Ordo Templi Orientis complains of copying in Groups
dmca.body:
Dear Google,
We regret to inform you of materials on Google Groups that infringe copyright. Please act appropriately in accordance with this notification to remove the infringing material from any servers under your control, including caches.

1. The infringed copyrighted works are linked to from the user page "Ordo Templi Orientis" located at
http://groups.google.com/group/Ordo-Templi-Orientis/

The subpages containing infringing materials are grouped for convenience of reference under lettered subheads:
(a) The following pages contain infringing material after the subheading "PART TWO".
